Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:07.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Like an angel that has no\Nsense of mercy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.61,0:00:14.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Rise, young boy, to the heavens\Nlike a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:26.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Cold winds, as blue as the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:30.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Tear open the door to\Nyour heart, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.25,0:00:33.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,But unknowing you seem, just\Nstaring at me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:38.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Standing there smiling serenely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:41.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Desperate, for something to touch...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:45.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,A moment of kindness like\Nthat in a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:48.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Your innocent eyes, have yet no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:51.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Of the path your destiny will follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:56.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,But someday you’ll become aware of...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:58.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Everything that you’ve got behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.16,0:01:03.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Your wings are for seeking out a new...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:06.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Future that only you can search for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:15.01,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,The cruel angel’s thesis enters through\Nthe window of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:18.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,If you should betray the chapel\Nof your memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:22.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,The cruel angel’s thesis bleeds through\Na portal like your pulsing blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:26.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,So, boy, stand tall and embrace\Nthe fire of the legend,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.18,0:01:30.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Opening,Embracing the universe like\Na blazing star!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:33.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, have you seen her yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.56,0:01:34.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!  Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:35.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Seen what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:37.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You dork, you haven’t seen the girl\Nwho studied overseas yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:38.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Girl who studied overseas?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.99,0:01:41.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, she’s in 8th grade, Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.13,0:01:44.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,She just transferred here last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.07,0:01:46.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,She’s hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:51.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Her name’s Asuka Langley Soryu,\Ndid you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.21,0:01:53.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, she’s so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:57.45,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Since she was raised over there but\Nborn here, do you think she\Nalready has a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.45,0:01:58.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:01.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I bet she broke up in Germany,\Nand she’s here in a foreign land...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:04.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...with a heart that can’t be mended.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:10.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.43,0:02:12.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...did you hear all the cat talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka!  Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:17.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,They’re just ignorant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:18.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thank you, come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:23.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,At least the pictures don’t\Nreveal her personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:25.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:27.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:28.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Guten Morgen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.81,0:02:30.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,G...guten Morgen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:33.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why so gloomy?  This is the gorgeous\NAsuka greeting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:36.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You should appreciate\Nyour good fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:38.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m the most popular girl in school!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:42.52,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, the other one’s here too, isn’t she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:43.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.53,0:02:47.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you, stupid?  I’m talking\Nabout the First Child, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:49.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, Ayanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:01.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.08,0:03:04.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You must be Rei Ayanami, the pilot\Nof the prototype.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:09.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m Asuka!  Asuka Langley Soryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:13.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m the designated pilot of Eva Unit 02.\NLet’s be good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:14.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:18.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because it’d be convenient.\NYou know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If I’m ordered to, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Talk about odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:26.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll say.  Are only weirdos\Nchosen to be pilots?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.21,0:03:37.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’ve lost some weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.55,0:03:38.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:40.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You must be enduring\Nan unrequited love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:43.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,How... did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.89,0:03:46.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:51.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...“a woman with a mole in the\Npathway of her tears is destined\Nto a life full of them.”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:55.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If you’re trying to put a move\Non me, I’m afraid you can’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There’s a very ugly face observing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.40,0:04:03.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Mr. Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:04.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:07.94,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re a little less discreet\Nthan I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:10.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He hasn’t ever been discreet in his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:14.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’ve finished handing over Unit 02,\Nhaven’t you?!  You should\Nbe leaving now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:18.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I just received orders this morning\Nthat I’ll be staying here “on loan.”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:20.06,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, we can hang around again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.39,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...just like we used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.39,0:04:23.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’ve got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.39,0:04:26.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Enemy attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:28.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We just got this report from the\Nbattle cruiser Haruna.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:32.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,“Have detected huge submerged object\Noff Kii peninsula.  Sending data.”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The data has been collated\Nand examined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.24,0:04:37.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Wavelength Pattern Blue.\NConfirmed to be an Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:39.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,All personnel, go to first stage alert.
