Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.08,0:04:50.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The recent battle severely damaged\NTokyo-3’s intercept system.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Only 26% of our defense capability\Nhas been restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.66,0:04:56.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,In addition, our operational capability\Nfor actual combat is virtually nil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:05:02.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Therefore, we’re going to have to\Nintercept the target at the water’s edge,\Nright before it makes landfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:06.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Units 01 and 02 will mount a\Ncoordinated attack in a series of waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:07.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,In other words, close in and take turns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.97,0:05:09.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:12.37,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This sucks.  My Japanese debut and\Nshe won’t let me handle it solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:14.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why do I have to bring you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.78,0:05:18.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,SOP.  Procedures, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:22.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, let me tell you something, just\Ndon’t get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.62,0:05:27.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,His selection as a pilot must have\Nbeen a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:43.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Two against one is not what I call\Na fair fight.  It’s not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:47.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We don’t get a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:49.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Survival takes priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:01.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Commence attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:04.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll handle this Angel!  You cover me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:05.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,C...cover you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.83,0:06:07.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ladies first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn it, don’t give me orders\Nyou dumb rookie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.54,0:06:17.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:31.69,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That wasn’t bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:36.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, Third Child, what did you\Nthink of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A fight should be clean and\Nelegant, without waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s this crap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:07:01.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Today, at 10:58.15 AM...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.48,0:07:05.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...Unit 01 was attacked\Nby Target Alpha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:08.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...which had separated from the other\Ntarget submerged 2 km off Suruga Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:12.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,At the same hour, same minute, plus 20\Nseconds, Unit 02 was halted by\NTarget Beta’s attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:15.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We have a comment from\NProject E chairperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.73,0:07:16.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.93,0:07:21.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is all your fault!  You totally\Nscrewed up my debut battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:25.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?  You’re\Nthe one who charged in there acting\Nlike an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:28.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Idiot?!  How dare you call me that?\NYou pathetic excuse for a combat pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.58,0:07:30.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re just a jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:33.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Look in the mirror!  You were in such a\Nrush to show off in combat that you\Ncompletely disregarded procedures!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What was that?  You look\Nlike a drowned rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}At 11:03 AM, NERV abandoned the...\N{\c&H00E3FE&}What was that?  You look\Nlike a drowned rat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}At 11:03 AM, NERV abandoned the...\N{\c&H00E3FE&}You... you can’t say that\Nkind of thing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You... you can’t say that\Nkind of thing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:43.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,...operation and transferred command\Nto the UN Secondary Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:45.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ve been humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.79,0:07:49.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,At 11:05 AM, the UN forces made\Nan attack with an N2 mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:53.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ll have to redraw the map again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,They succeeded in burning off 28% of\Ntarget’s structural substance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:56.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Did they kill it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:59.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is merely temporary relief.  The\Nsecond attack is just a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.98,0:08:03.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,At least we have time to reorganize\Nand regroup.  You can’t ask for\Nmore than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.95,0:08:05.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Listen up, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:08.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do you know what your job is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Piloting Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:10.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Your job is to defeat the Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:16.06,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,NERV does not exist to make grotesque\Ndisplays like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.06,0:08:18.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Therefore, you two must cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why should we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.70,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:26.30,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why does everyone get so angry here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:28.90,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s because adults are much too\Naware of their credibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Um, where’s Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:35.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Clearing things up.  The person in\Ncharge exists to take responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:40.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Here are the protests and damage\Nreports from the bureau concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is a bill from the UN...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.95,0:08:45.16,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and here you have a complaint from\Nthe Public Relations Department as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:47.62,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Read them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:50.06,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can tell what they say without looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:52.69,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,“If you’re going to fight,\Ndo it here,” right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:54.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.03,0:08:57.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll do it as soon as we take\Ncare of this Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.67,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I swear I will destroy that Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:02.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Vice-Commander is pretty angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.67,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’ll almost certainly be demoted\Nif you embarrass him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:10.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It was just good luck within bad luck\Nthat Commander Ikari wasn’t here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If he’d been here, you’d have been fired\Nbefore he ever saw these papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:17.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, have you brought me an\Nidea to help save my job?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:19.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:21.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I thank you, Dr. Ritsuko Akagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s good to have a friend\None can count on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:28.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, I’m not the one who’ll\Nbe saving my old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:30.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is Kaji’s idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:32.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.05,0:09:51.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m home!  Not that anyone’s here,\Nof course, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.76,0:09:54.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:56.49,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t be so rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.49,0:09:58.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Those are my personal belongings!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:00.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You!  What in blazes are you\Ndoing in my house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why are you STILL here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:05.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:08.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, you’ve been dumped\Nfor the new model!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.70,0:10:12.11,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato will be living with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:16.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Of course, that’s a much more logical\Nchoice when you consider\Nmy superior abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:18.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Although honestly, I’d rather\Nlive with Kaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:22.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Say, just why are Japanese houses\Nso small anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not even half of my stuff fits!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.82,0:10:32.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,And Japanese sure don’t have\Nany sense of privacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:36.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,How can they live in a room without\Nlocks?  Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:39.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s because the Japanese way is to\Nconsider the priorities and needs of\Nothers before one’s own.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:41.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:44.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,How are you?  You two are going\Nto get along real well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:45.67,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is all preparation for\Nthe next operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:49.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:52.01,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There is only one way to destroy\Nthe Seventh Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.01,0:10:56.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A simultaneous two-point attack\Non each target’s core while its\Ncomponents are separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:11:02.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,In other words, an attack by two Evas\Nwith perfectly synchronized timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.66,0:11:06.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Cooperation and coordination between\Nthe two of you will be paramount.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:11.37,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Therefore, I want the two\Nof you to live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:17.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No way!  “A boy and a girl should\Nnever sleep under one roof after\Nthe age of seven”!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:19.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Angel is currently restoring itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.94,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It will begin its second assault\Nin six days, there’s no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But it’s impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.15,0:11:28.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now we have a way to\Nmake it possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:33.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The master attack pattern will be\Nchoreographed using this music.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.79,0:11:36.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,In six days, as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.30,0:11:49.94,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m worried about Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:52.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He’s been gone three days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, there’s the class rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.35,0:11:58.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Two of the three stooges.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:01.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:04.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,To offer condolences to Miss Soryu.\NWhat about you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,To offer condolences to Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why did you stop here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:19.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Y...you’ve betrayed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:21.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You look like two peas in a pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.84,0:12:24.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:29.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Neither can we.  It’s all Misato’s fault!\NWe have to eat, breathe and\Nsleep together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re living in sin!  How awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:34.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  It’s not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then just what is it like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hi, welcome everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:41.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why don’t you explain all this to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:46.69,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You should have told us that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:49.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,How is the coordination coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:51.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, so much for synchronization!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:01.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I could never sink down to the pathetic\Nlevel this animated turnip lives at!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:03.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If you ask me, this whole\Nidea is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:06.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then you give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:08.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But you don’t have anyone\Nelse, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:10.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:10.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, ma’am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why don’t you try?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:13.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, ma’am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:27.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It looks like I should alter the operation\Nto make a pair of Shinji and Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:34.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  I can’t stand this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:35.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:40.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:42.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Even the Devil cries sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.12,0:13:45.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’ve got to follow her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:52.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You made her cry!  It’s your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:02.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:03.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.31,0:14:09.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:11.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have to pilot the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:16.45,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve got no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:18.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:21.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No matter what, I’ll put Rei and\NMisato to shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:24.06,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You don’t have to squash them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:27.30,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re being too simplistic, even if\Nyou are a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I must avenge myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:31.30,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...my pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.01,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s a matter of honor now, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:15.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Where’s Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.61,0:15:18.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,At work.  She called earlier.\NShe’ll be there all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:22.52,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, that means we’re all\Nalone tonight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.23,0:15:38.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is the impenetrable “Wall\Nof Jericho,” Third Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:42.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Take one step over this wall\Nand you’ll be a dead man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:45.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,And now, it’s time to go to bed, children!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:50.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why do Japanese sleep on the floor?\NThis is so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.58,0:17:03.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:15.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re just a child yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:18.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, somebody’s watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:19.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who’s watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.00,0:17:20.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Someb...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:45.06,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  There’s nothing between\Nus anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.69,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t do that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.69,0:17:49.70,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But your lips didn’t say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:54.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Which one should I trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:56.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Your lips or your words?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:19.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re unusually sober today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.60,0:18:24.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.93,0:18:27.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Work?  Or a man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.14,0:18:29.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:32.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Still in love?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:35.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t be ridiculous!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who’d want that idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.25,0:18:45.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I was young, and it’s still the biggest\Nblemish on my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:49.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I meant that he may still like you.\NDid I scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.79,0:18:51.16,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why you lousy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:53.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re only proving my hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:56.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why don’t you go with your feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.90,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s not like it’s still eight years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.90,0:19:02.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It hasn’t changed.  Not a bit.\NHe’s still immature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:07.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I’ve got to get to work.\NTomorrow is D-Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.19,0:19:22.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Target has broken through the\Nfinal defense line at Gora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.49,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.49,0:19:26.49,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We won’t fail this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:29.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Spread your AT fields as soon\Nas the music starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then follow the operation\Nchoreography.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.17,0:19:32.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you two ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:36.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The target has entered the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:40.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Just remember Shinji, full power,\Nmaximum performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.47,0:19:43.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know that.  We’ll finish in 62 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:46.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Target entering ground zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:47.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Detach external power cables.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:51.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:05.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Confirmation.  Both Evas are\Noperational.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:11.37,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.67,0:21:16.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.79,0:21:18.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you doing on my Unit 02?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:21.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?  You’re\Nthe one who fell on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re the one who lost\Nhis timing first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:24.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re always so slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:29.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What were you doing, staying up so\Nlate last night?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:32.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Image training for today’s battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:36.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Liar!  I know you tried to kiss\Nme while I was sleeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You cheat!  You were awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:43.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh!  I was just kidding!\NDid you really kiss me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:46.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, I didn’t!  I stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:48.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Pervert!  Fiend!  Idiot!\NI can’t believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:53.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You caused it by calling for your\Nmother and sleepwalking!
Dialogue: 3,0:21:54.81,0:21:57.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,Those kids are embarrassing us again.
